##The irony of life

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
February 28,2020.

The Sixth Day of the second lunar month.

Wuhan is closed for thirty-seven days.

The Gates of Heaven are sealed, Day thirty-six.

It was raining, and the retreat continued. As the days dwindled, Milan Kundera's "happiness is repeating the same thing" became a recipe for self-soothing at home. The senses are paralyzed by repetition, and the pain is chewed to dullness. You have to remind yourself that you can continue to be conscious of a little tingling in your life while you're going through the plague, experiencing history, and challenging yourself.

Albert Camus said, "The first trick an author learns is how to translate what he feels into what he wants to feel. The success of the first few times is accidental, but then the accidental must be replaced by talent."So I have to admit that I am Jiang Yan.
